rocco</strong></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"gallery\" class=\"gallery\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#f5d7a0\">Galerie</div>\n      <h2>L'œil dans l'assiette</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#aaa\">Quelques instants capturés chez nous.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gal-grid\"><div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNA2L-UW-xKvc3rHU2mJfw2hhk-owK4QQ7yQUmt=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"La Pelle à Pizza - Casablanca\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHrwi5DdqXmlZpL2hcpPoRj0Qtc9X6gx2jxthX72q4MRFGXr1yhVami-4nxho2kN6ekemkLfrsZFsldPw1rdp5vnnbX6jA3Y0AYUbmQrs7N8klONXo4XOhJEbh9Bo-hnXoS2XFuhKFhJgq4=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"La Pelle à Pizza - Casablanca\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/_5KscoIr1nEA67kVzs8DSSWsYGRWtLv8l7fFUZtEnxyoVLp7ccdDVI_DpRKZ4fal3CKHbUUlKreuttCllETupJkFNR_sTwWH7K_LNFSBpUCcDg9SorkaujaDQP44q9ypYur63e0mpzUItO1_FaE2bPxA4iAbmg=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"La Pelle à Pizza - Casablanca\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/SCxrUgfxl7ft-d6blIIfo3bunJlbF8n3Wi8QfEKLe1DvghF-dpOoMtVnBroMtCHiijIqPLoJNxFVJZfw8khcOx_vCXBWXR-aIVqprNGirAytdplIfCLfEqEQk3UTzWxbf_EuoMuxXb6MSIuG920DuN3r7zLkbQ=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"La Pelle à Pizza - Casablanca\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/8IalFC2IeHvaMhmQuJFxFntP_-YvNiCQIdDUU2ZaxZ8EZ16vMKU9L5WzemQfhsQjFy6V62uZs0tSbDxnxM1wH4VVFeczhHhhMcjSufO1xa3kQkKgTU3EXd83XdLqLDT7c5x6Hj5W0c85fQbQCJW7ZbVnG333Iw=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"La Pelle à Pizza - Casablanca\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/wFrYClpXjrbhcRsgyGOPbweU7ScT7Dx7Ok2RBG2RZbLch9whmgnLD4zUY